name: Boudica (Fate) LoRA
description:
Boudica (Fate) LoRA

LoRA request queue: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DXjs-96citoEa4NPWWxm4o92kQyrJpgdXQGWQg65oiM/edit?usp=sharing

This model was trained using 32 images of Boudica. It was trained on the NAI model so it should work with most anime based models. Some images were NSFW so you might get those sometimes, but mostly it was sfw.

Recommended weight is between 0.7 and 0.9

Trigger word is Boudica, sadly I mainly found images of her first ascension (ppl really like her first ascension) so you probably will only get that one.

Example images were generated using AOM2 hard with 30 steps, then upscaled with low strength and 150 steps.
